  "texts": [
    "F-Stat (Partial) reports the F-statistic on the partial effect of Coworker Encouragement (EBS).",
    "The table is based on all completed responses from workplaces with at least two respondents from the 2024 survey linked to registry data.",
    "In Section E.5.2, we estimate how employer encouragement affects the impact of AI chatbots, contrasting the effects of workers' self-reported encouragement with those of their coworkers'.",
    "To ensure the effects are measured on comparable scales, and not attenuated by measurement error, we present 2SLS estimates for the impact of coworker-reported employer encouragement:",
    "Encouraged i = π ′ X j,-i + α × Encouraged j,-i + ε 1i (71)"
